Formulae of project

For Duration, D = ( From Project_Duration (End - Start) )

Y = (TotalCash_inflow * D ) - ( TotalCash_outflow * D)

1. Needed Capital = TotalCash_outflow * 3

2. Payback Period = Needed Capital / Y = X years

3. Net Present Value = Y / ( 1 + 0.02 ) ^ D

4. Profitability index = Net Present Value / Needed Capital
